  "name": "Rangeland Condition Monitoring Assessment and Projection (RCMAP)",
  "description": "RCMAP provides annual rangeland vegetation component fractional cover and related products across western North America derived from Landsat imagery. Components include bare ground, herbaceous, litter, shrub, sagebrush, tree (and related component/trend products), supporting rangeland monitoring and assessment from 1985 to present.",
